  "_comment": "Wave 4b flag normalization. Maps T005 gate flags (canonical: flag.T00X_<slug>) to the upstream outcome_flag names actually emitted by T001-T004 quests. Resolver checks alias[gate_flag] -> set of upstream flags; if any are set, gate is open. Rather than churn 100+ inline flag strings, the world-agent should consult this table at gate-eval time. New work should emit canonical flag.T00X_* names directly.",
